snippet.title: Pipe Push Paradise - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Out January 2018 on Windows/Mac/Linux via Steam/Itch

http://toboggan.work
http://store.steampowered.com/app/721390/Pipe_Push_Paradise/
https://toboggan.itch.io/pipe-push-paradise

Pipe Push Paradise is a difficult open world puzzle game about plumbing. You've arrived on a lonely island faced with a hero's calling. Rise to the occasion (push pipes around) and restore this paradise to its former glory.
